data.description: Wonderfully updated Colonial ready for you to call home! Bright, airy and great for entertaining. As you step though the front door you will be greeted with a large open living room with a central fireplace. This opens onto the dining area featuring a wall of beautiful built-ins and leads into the spacious kitchen with  stainless steel appliances. Rounding out the main floor is laundry and a half bath. The second floor is where you will find your 3 bedrooms all with hardwoods and plenty of closet space, main bath and walk up attic. With it's great backyard, situated on a level lot in a quiet neighborhood, this house is ready for you to  settle in, get ready for spring, and enjoy. All you have to do is move in! Schedule your showing today, it will go fast!
